  affects the NavPanelHotTrackFont object. For example, when NavPanelHotTrackFontOptions includes
  hoPreserveColor, all property changes in Font are copied to NavPanelHotTrackFont except Color
  changes.

  Note that hoFollowFont must be included for any properties to be copied at all.
See Also
  Font

