  Occurs when the user clicks the splitter.
Description
  Use the OnSplitterClick event handler to respond when the user clicks the splitter.
See Also
  TJvCustomNavigationPane.OnSplitterDblClick, TJvCustomNavigationPane.OnSplitterMouseDown,
  TJvCustomNavigationPane.OnSplitterMouseMove, TJvCustomNavigationPane.OnSplitterMouseUp

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomNavigationPane.OnSplitterDblClick
Summary
