  a close button is visible, clicking it triggers the <LINK OnClose> event but does not actually hide
  the panel (you will have to implement this behavior yourself).
See Also
  TJvCustomNavPaneToolPanel.OnClose

----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCustomNavPaneToolPanel.Colors
Summary
  Contains the color settings of the control.
Description
